msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F6</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>स्थानपट्टिका</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>संपादनीयं स्थानम्</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes the location bar between the two modes; the <link linkend=\"location-"
"bar-bread-crumb\">bread crumb mode</link> and the <link linkend=\"location-"
"bar-editable\">editable mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"द्वयोः मोडयोः मध्ये स्थानपट्टिकां परिवर्तयति; the<link linkend=\"location-bar-bread-"
"crumb\"> ब्रेड क्रम्ब मोड</link> तथा<link linkend=\"location-bar-editable\"> "
"सम्पादनयोग्य मोड</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Location Bar</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Replace Location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>स्थानपट्टिका</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>प्रतिस्थापनं कुर्वन्तु स्थान</guimenuitem> इति"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches the location bar to <link linkend=\"location-bar-editable"
"\">editable mode</link>, if necessary, and selects the location such that it "
"can be replaced quickly."
msgstr ""
"स्थानपट्टिकां प्रति परिवर्तयति<link linkend=\"location-bar-editable\"> सम्पादनयोग्य "
"मोड</link> , यदि आवश्यकं भवति, तथा च स्थानं चिनोति यथा शीघ्रं प्रतिस्थापयितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2047
#, no-c-format
