msgstr "वर्तमानपुटे प्राधान्यं अन्वेषणसाधनं उद्घाटयति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Files</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सञ्चिकानां तुलनां कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compare the currently selected files or folders with &kompare;. This action "
